Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:01:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郭嘉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想再像以前那样在街上向女孩搭讪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再痛痛快快地打架
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 好处总是被你抢跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 孟德那家伙也相当受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我不知道为什么 老是和男人泡在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能指挥进攻南阳的战略
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在没心情参与战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说南阳首领孙策伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和作为斗士的你并非生人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是很有缘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很笨 但她是个不错的家伙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说孙策和母亲一同寄住在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同为南阳斗士的周瑜家中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传言说你和孙策母亲的关系也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想攻其不备 连他身边的周瑜一同打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该是最适人选
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保险起见 我先把话说在前头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次南阳战的指挥 是曹操大人的敕命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是孟德下的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是孟德下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:04:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不直接跟我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 这种做法本来就与我性格不和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳头对拳头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.15,0:04:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂正正的较量才是斗士的根本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曹操大人现在正躲在地下闭门不出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实传达给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是冰之军师大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使郭嘉死了 表情也毫无变化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那是孟德的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要用我的做法办事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:05:01.11,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四话　二龙邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你从房顶跳下来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又干这种蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 不能再轻点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没礼数
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 来吃晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩…玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说是玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个白痴女儿 竟然说了不该说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分啊 真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个纸门 昨天才刚把纸换好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许昌逐步镇压了关东
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我校的主力吕蒙却去向不明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左慈也躲在山里不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘宁还在住院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在南阳的四天王差了三个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果成为了曹操的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能不能保护好伯符啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公谨 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的教训太严格了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能因为这个就逃到我房间里来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想小便
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厕所在那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腿特别疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带我去啦 公谨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 大不了在这里解决
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公谨 没纸了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以不擦就出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿过来 你老老实实地等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 像个小孩似的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是打破了纸门就暴怒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是周瑜公谨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是… 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是乌丸族首领
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫蜴顿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜴顿?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 你们是许昌的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公谨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 我生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是还礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景色不错啊 小霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不逃跑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话真希望都脱光以后再干掉你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深更半夜的突然跑到人家家里来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还在人家上厕所的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说都太失礼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么失不失礼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不也派吕蒙子明偷袭了成都学园吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事再讲得具体些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是战争啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 这么晚了还吵吵嚷嚷的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆不想受伤的话 还是闪一边去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吴荣 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来 你踏到了决不可践踏的地雷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里异常兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁是老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈果然很强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听说她妈妈这么厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里还是先撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们乌丸族为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许随便行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭一年级的小子想单独攻击君主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早了一百年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小{\fn幼圆}{\fs25}{\b1}惇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于这边的差错给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…别在意了 小{\fn幼圆}{\fs25}{\b1}惇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的关系都这么好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:45.38,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还可以努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:45.38,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生从这里开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好久没像这样运动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还是敌不过年纪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曹操果然还是盯上了南阳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想干突袭这种肮脏的行径
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想堂堂正正地在战斗上决一胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是真正的斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符 你刚刚的态度怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在客人面前打瞌睡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要睡的话回自己房间睡去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 夏侯{\fn幼圆}{\fs25}{\b1}惇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,争斗是无法避免的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的伙伴甘宁杀了许昌的干部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我只是不想用卑鄙的手段复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的到底是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曹操已经开始攻击南阳了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和预定计划一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们竟然私下见了面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏侯渊… 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是郭嘉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郭嘉死前将你托付给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郭嘉死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被暗杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙玉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.26,0:14:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郭嘉说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙玉拥有能够改变曹操命运的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变曹操大人的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将生命献给了曹操孟德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会将龙玉弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救赎 荣耀和力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆属于我神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的裁决是真实而正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗杀了许昌郭嘉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是南阳的斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成都正面临危机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 总欠关羽人情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全没什么好表现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是那样的笨蛋斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦觉醒了 我们就拿她没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次觉醒 玄德都会逐渐为自己的力量所毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须要加油保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是哪里的什么人来 我都不会再输了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 这里是成都学园吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:16:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为搞错地方 跑到神社里来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊 校服没看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我? 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张飞 休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是转校生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前是哪个学校的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是以前 我现在也在南阳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你是南阳的!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张…张飞 你要干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然从正面堂堂正正地进来 我就夸奖你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在生什么气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是来找人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用多说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你非要打的话 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张飞 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 张飞又要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说我会输吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.57,0:18:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人不爽的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想张飞要是受伤了就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是差不多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 要打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不打呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然打了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公谨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说她是伯符?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫伯符吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是孙策伯符 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不许你碰玄德一根手指
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关…关羽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关羽…云长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么最近常见到好久不见的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吕布 你改变了命运
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和关东的霸王董卓同归于尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底能不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出和你相同的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有沉睡在龙玉中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够抑制住三位王体内的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才想要让刘备玄德觉醒以尝试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟连我自身…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只封印了的左眼也产生了反应
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你 我像往常那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将压制龙的符缝在了纱布里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那只眼睛会散布诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是邪眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.30,0:20:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是符的力量耗尽了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.93,0:20:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是为了将孙策从龙的控制中解放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 是否应该将这个交给孙策
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在还在犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:20:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救赎 荣耀和力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆属于我神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的裁决是真实而正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有神的仆人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.62,0:21:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有畏惧神的人们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一同赞美我神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忏悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.57,0:23:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位观众 怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.06,0:23:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成熟又成熟 且不断朝着美的霸业前进的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.09,0:23:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 吴荣的大人魅力怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.74,0:23:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不会输给那些稚嫩的小女生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.37,0:23:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕对方是初中的古典少女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是使用日本刀的高中生美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是幼女谋士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集　一骑当千{\fnSimhei\fs25}Dragon Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.20,0:23:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗士无惨
